<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If you try to create an XML config using a multidimensional array and the keys are numeric, the value is an array, there gets a fatal error on string-convertion.</p>

<p>Example
{quote}

{quote}
creates this array:
{quote}
array('notification' =&gt;array('adress' =&gt;array(0 =&gt; array('name'=&gt;'firstname lastname','mail'=&gt;'mail@domain.de'),1 =&gt; array('name'=&gt;'firstname2 lastname2','mail'=&gt;'mail2@domain.de'))));
{quote}</p>

<p>// FIXME Zend/Config/Writer/Xml.php line (182)
$child = $parent-&gt;addChild($branchName {color:red}-,(string) $value-{color});</p>

